sentences: Denis Murphy (14 November 1910 – 7 April 1974) was an Irish fiddler and traditional musician.
Murphy emigrated to the United States, and in 1942 married Julie Mary Sheehan.
They returned often to Ireland and returned permanently to Lisheen in 1965.
